column2: Sunny and west to southwest wind.
High waves made underwater visibility difficult. Weather partly cloudy- strong wind from west.  Sun was shining at time of reading.
Sky clear- light breeze from the west.  Water very green.
Clear sky- light wind from north-northwest.
Wind from south- southwest- sky clear- low temp. in the 20s day before - 50s at time of sample.
In process of installing lake level gauge.
Slight overcast- temp 60 F.  Slight ripple on lake.
Site 3- lots of algae in water (or minute species of  ) .
Algae blooms- sunny- bright.  Slight ripple.
Sunny.  Big ripple.  Lots of tree seeds on lake.
Sunny- slight ripple- algae blooms abounding.
Algae bloom- heavy boat traffic on 7/4
Lots of algae blooms in water- temp is in the high 40's.
Sunny- few algal blooms- heavy ripple on surface.
Clear day- no algae blooms.  Water level: up 6" from 1992
Algae blooms prevalent. Water level: up 6"
Algae blooms- heavy ripple. Water level: up 6"
Windy- cool- algal blooms evident. Water level: up 6"- same as August
Algal blooms-looks like lake turned over!
Lots of pine pollen on lake.
Lots of jet skis on lake today!
Lots of pollen + algae blooms.  Cloudy w/slight ripple.
Some algae bloom- lots of pollen from pine trees
The crawfish are back- they stopped trapping them last year.  Everyone is remarking on the water clarity.
Heavy ripple- cloudy day- loons on the lake- baby eagle chased by sea gulls landed on lake.
Algae blooms visible- saw eagle and loons.
Algal blooms- saw 2 eagles and 2 loons.
Sunny afternoon- 60 degrees.  Loons on lake
Saw baby loon.  Small mouth bass fry evident.Water level: Up a little
Loon- seagull- mallards observed.  Profusion of algae blooms.
Cloudy. algae blooms. loons and eagles.
Northwest wind- sunny and clear.  Slight chop.
Windy- SW 15-20 mph- partial overcast to cloudy- rain on 5/13
SW wind 5 mph- no recent rain. High clouds (few). Chop
Very choppy- no rain- sunny- windy.
Slight chop- partially sunny.  Wind 5 mph NE.  Recent rain 11 days ago.
Clear- sunny- no wind.  Recent rain 6 days ago.
Clear- sunny- 5 mph wind. Slight shop. No rain for 10 days.
Clear- sunny. 8 mph- slight chop.  No rain 2 weeks.
Clear- sunny- 2 mph.  Rain within 5 days.
slight chop- sunny. NE wind at 7 MPH. Recent rain within 24 hours.
Choppy- sunny. W wind 5 MPH. Rainy weather previous 6 hours.
NE wind 3 MPH. Recent rain within last 6 days. Partially overcast. Not choppy.
High clouds- SW wind 10 MPH. Recent rain August 12- 2004. Quite Choppy.
Sunny- clear- very choppy. West wind 10 MPH. Recent rain on October 1.
Sunny. Light west wind - 5 MPH.- Last rain six days ago.
Sunny- no wind. Last rain 9 days ago.
Partly cloudy to overcast. Wind 3 MPH- E-SE. Recent rain 0.4 inches.
Sunny- chop. Rain 96 hours ago. South wind 5 MPH.
last rain 72 hours ago. Sunny- clear and calm.
last rain 20 hours ago. Partly cloudy- very windy. Wind at least 12 to 15 MPH. Hard to hold boat.
last rain 72 hours ago. Sunny- north wind at 15 MPH. Whitecaps.
Last rain 96 hours ago. Sunny- very windy. North wind at 15 MPH.
cloudy and overcast. North wind at 3 MPH. Last rain 6 days ago.
Last rain 5 days. Sunny- slight chop- wind 5 MPH
Last rain 11 days ago- partly sunny. South wind 8 MPH. Chop.
Last rain 24 hours ago. Sunny- North wind 2 MPH- slight chop.
Last rain 48 hours ago. Sunny and calm.
Wind 5 MPH from the NW. No rain for 11 days. Slight chop to water. Clouds and sun mixed.  Note:  adhesive on secchi disk was not removed- this may affect this reading.
NW wind 3 to 5 MPH. Last rain 40 hours prior. Slight chop- scattered clouds.

overcast and sunny. Last rain- a sprinkle- an hour ago. NE wind at 5 MPH.
Partly cloudy- no wind. Last rain 5 days ago. Very calm. Lots of pollen.
Sunny. Last rain 72 hours ago. Calm water. More algae observed.
Sunny. Last rain 48 hours ago (1.2 inches). More algae. Slight wind to calm.
Sunny. Wind 5 MPH. Last rain 6 days ago.
Sunny- partial clouds. NW wind 3 MPH. Recent rain- 5 hours ago.
Sunny and clear. SE wind 4 MPH. Last rain 1 week ago.
last rain was 72 - 96 hours previous. Cloudy- slight chop. Wind 1-3 MPH.
Partly cloudy. Last rain 12 hours ago. Slight chop- wind 5-8 MPH.
Sunny. Last rain 7 days ago. Wind 5-8 MPH.
Cloudy and sunny. Last rain 12 days ago. Wind 3-5 MPH.
NE wind 3 MPH. Rain in last 48 hours. Scattered clouds.
Wind 5-10 MPH from SE. Rain within the last 18 hours. Overcast

last rain was 10 days ago. Partly sunny. Wind 1-2 MPH.
last rain 12 days ago. Sunny. Wind 3 MPH.

NW wind at 5 MPH. Last rain 96 hours ago. Sunny.
NW wind at 2-3 MPH. recent rain - 56 hours ago. Sunny.

Slight chop. Sunny- wind 1-2 MPH. last rain 36 hours ago.
Recent rain 48 hrs. Very windy. Lake is churned up.
Sunny- calm. Heavy rain 3-4 days before.
Partly sunny. Light- variable wind. Haze and smoke from Canadian wildfires.
Partly sunny to sunny. Light- steady breeze.
